name: Sub Threshold CX 2min
description:
This is a challenging session that builds upon the earlier work of steady sub-threshold efforts. By challenging your ability to process lactate at near-threshold power, you will increase your time to exhaustion and increase endurance. All this is achieved with a 30min steady state effort that dips briefly into the realms of VO2max.
